articles.author: Stephen Collinson
articles.title: The pulsating state politics that could shape America more than Trump's legal woes - CNN
articles.description: Donald Trump may be getting all the headlines, but partisan struggles in state capitals across the country may do far more to change America than the drama surrounding the first ex-president to be charged with a crime.
